Description: An advanced resource scheduler and load balancer for Proxmox clusters
 ProxLB balances VM and container workloads across Proxmox cluster nodes,
 respecting affinity/anti-affinity rules, maintenance modes, and resource
 reservations. Optionally uses a CP-SAT solver for mathematically optimal
 placement. All Python dependencies including the solver are bundled.
